你能够调用以下的API:
[['PensionPlanSearch.find_plans', {'name': 'PensionPlanSearch.find_plans', 'description': 'This function searches for pension plans based on type and location.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'type', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The type of pension plan, e.g., retirement, corporate.'}, {'name': 'location', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The location where the plan will be applied.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'plans', 'description': 'A list of up to three matching pension plans, each with an ID, type, and provider.'}]}], ['PensionPlanSearch.get_plan_details', {'name': 'PensionPlanSearch.get_plan_details', 'description': 'This function retrieves detailed information about a specific pension plan given its ID.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'planId', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'The ID of the pension plan.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'details', 'description': 'Detailed information about the plan, including benefits, contributions, and terms.'}]}], ['PensionPlanSearch.get_historical_data', {'name': 'PensionPlanSearch.get_historical_data', 'description': 'This function retrieves historical data for a specific pension plan for a given year.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'planId', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'The ID of the pension plan.'}, {'name': 'year', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'The year for which historical data is requested.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'historicalData', 'description': 'Historical data for the plan, including performance and contributions.'}]}], ['PensionPlanSearch.get_market_data', {'name': 'PensionPlanSearch.get_market_data', 'description': 'This function retrieves real-time market data for a specific pension plan.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'planId', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'The ID of the pension plan.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'marketData', 'description': 'Real-time market data for the plan, including current performance and trends.'}]}], ['PensionPlanSearch.get_plan_recommendations', {'name': 'PensionPlanSearch.get_plan_recommendations', 'description': 'This function provides recommendations for a specific pension plan based on its ID.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'planId', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'The ID of the pension plan.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'recommendations', 'description': 'Recommendations for the plan, including potential improvements and alternatives.'}]}]]
请生成一个解决用户问题的计划，计划应该是一个行为列表，每个行为的格式如下:

[{
    // 动作的ID
    "id": number;
    // 动作要调用的API名称
    "name": string;
    // 当前API的参数输入(JSON格式)
    "args": "str(Record<string, any>)";
}, ...
]

你可以在计划中想象参数的值，这些指令将按顺序执行。
例如，如果你想调用 `PensionPlanSearch.find_plans` 并传入 `type` 和 `location`，你可以写下面的计划:

[{
    "id": 0,
    "name": "PensionPlanSearch.find_plans",
    "args": "{'type': 'retirement', 'location': 'California'}",
}, ...
]

这些参数将在执行时被替换为真实的值。请注意，参数应该是一个字符串，而不是一个字典。
请在字典的参数中使用 ''，在其他地方使用 ""，不要打印值为 None 或 null 的参数。

你应该只生成一个 JSON 格式的计划列表。列表应该是完整的计划列表，不要有 `...`。
不要生成任何解释 JSON 的文本。
